        <message>A maximum of 5 days of relocation leave is granted to a colleague who has to transfer at Absa's request and that transfer results in relocation. 
Only one day of relocation leave is provided to colleagues who transfer and relocate at their own request. 
Please note that you cannot use relocation leave to move house as this will be annual leave. 

You are required to speak to your line manager before requesting relocation leave.</message>
